query:
SELECT v.id, v.formandoId, v.valorTotal, v.valorLiquido, v.excluido,
       v.dataVenda,
       DATE_FORMAT(v.dataVenda, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%i:%s') as data_formatada,
       f.nome as formando_nome,
       f.turmaId,
       t.codigo as turma_codigo
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id
LEFT JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id
WHERE v.dataVenda BETWEEN '2026-06-14 00:00:00' AND '2026-06-15 23:59:59'
  AND v.excluido = 0
  AND (f.turmaId IS NULL OR t.codigo IS NULL)
ORDER BY v.id
